{"tid":1234318,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成功要有無比既耐性同堅持","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T01:37:32.000Z","uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0b83972fb20efe49a00f3f8b43a1f4ad8833d182","tid":1234318,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"就算你用android機定iphone，相信你都唔會完全否定iphone 10年既轉變。有好多功能係由一班工程師不段努力咁創造出來。就算有部分功能係由其他系統抄襲返來，推出前都要不斷測試、改良，先可以推出。推出左又可能市場反應差就要收回。<br />\n<br />\n社會運動都係一樣，無可能一步就成功。況且我地無一個好似蘋果教主咁既人領導，十樣野可能有十樣野都唔會成功。咁樣並唔係放棄既理由，只要大家堅持可能試到第一百種方法就會成功。<br />\n<br />\n請原諒我1999，由細到大都做CDROM。因為見到出面好多分化POST，希望大家唔好中計。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。同時亦都要互相幫助，互相體諒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/17/091758_9c8fd6b8f9780d2d0303b47a106cc942.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F091758_9c8fd6b8f9780d2d0303b47a106cc942.png&h=27b08cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://m.hindustantimes.com/interactives/visual-history-of-the-iphone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hindustantimes.com%2Finteractives%2Fvisual-history-of-the-iphone%2F&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWkqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=577b2e73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hindustantimes.com/interactives/visual-history-of-the-iphone/</a>"}]}